# Learning How To Learn: How do you juggle life and learning?

* Write a weekly todo list (*the week before*)
* Write a daily todo list (*the night before*)
* Include something physical on your list, like "go for a walk", or "clean the bathroom".
* *Plan your quitting time as well as your starting time*.
* Reflect on your lists and make your tasks more realistic if you consistently fail to complete your list on time.
* Planning healthy leisure time is important, don't overwork yourself.
* Eat your frogs first! (1 pomodoro minimum)


